<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">

<!-- Important for browser compatibility -->
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Wix Help Center - TLP Compliance</title>

<style>

/* ===== GLOBAL FIXES ===== */
*,
*::before,
*::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f5f7fa;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}

/* ===== NAVBAR ===== */
.navbar {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
    padding: 15px 20px;

    display: flex;
    display: -webkit-flex;

    justify-content: space-between;
    -webkit-justify-content: space-between;

    align-items: center;
    -webkit-align-items: center;

    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.logo {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 18px;
}

.nav-links span {
    margin-left: 15px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* ===== SEARCH ===== */
.search-section {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 25px 15px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
}

.search-box {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 500px;
    padding: 12px 15px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    font-size: 14px;
    outline: none;
}

/* ===== LAYOUT ===== */
.main {
    display: flex;
    display: -webkit-flex;

    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 0 15px;

    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* ===== SIDEBAR ===== */
.sidebar {
    width: 250px;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

.sidebar h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.sidebar a {
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.sidebar a:hover {
    color: #116dff;
}

/* ===== CONTENT ===== */
.content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

/* ===== BUTTON ===== */
.button-container {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 30px;
}

.btn {
    background-color: #116dff;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;

    display: inline-block;

    transition: 0.3s;
    -webkit-transition: 0.3s;
}

.btn:hover {
    background-color: #0d5be1;
}

/* ===== RELATED ===== */
.related {
    margin-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-top: 20px;
}

.related h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
}

.related a {
    display: block;
    color: #116dff;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
}

/* ===== FOOTER ===== */
.footer {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #777;
    padding: 20px;
}

/* ===== MOBILE ===== */
@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .sidebar {
        width: 100%;
    }

    .content {
        width: 100%;
    }
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<div class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">WIX Help Center</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <span>Help Topics</span>
        <span>Account</span>
        <span>Contact</span>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- SEARCH -->
<div class="search-section">
    <input class="search-box" type="text" placeholder="Search for help...">
</div>

<!-- MAIN -->
<div class="main">

    <!-- SIDEBAR -->
    <div class="sidebar">
        <h3>Help Topics</h3>
        <a href="#">Getting Started</a>
        <a href="#">Account & Billing</a>
        <a href="#">Security & Compliance</a>
        <a href="#">Website Management</a>
        <a href="#">Domains</a>
        <a href="#">Email Services</a>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Threat-Level Protection (TLP) Compliance Requirement</h1>

        <p>As part of an ongoing platform-wide security initiative, Wix has introduced a mandatory Threat-Level Protection (TLP) compliance verification process...</p>

        <p>TLP represents a structured set of security configurations designed to protect critical information...</p>

        <p>Websites identified as potentially non-compliant are required to take immediate action...</p>

        <p>To facilitate compliance, users may connect with a designated specialist...</p>

        <p>All flagged websites must complete verification within the specified compliance period...</p>

        <p>Users are therefore strongly advised to act promptly...</p>

        <div class="button-container">
            <a class="btn" href="mailto:thesupremedigitals@gmail.com?subject=TLP%20Configuration%20Assistance&body=Hi,%0D%0AI%20have%20been%20direct%20by%20Wix%20to%20reach%20out%20for%20assistance%20regarding%20my%20website%20Threat-Level%20Protection%20(TLP)%20configuration.%0D%0AHow%20can%20you%20help%20me?">
                Contact Specialist
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="related">
            <h3>Related Articles</h3>
            <a href="#">Understanding Wix Security Standards</a>
            <a href="#">How to Configure Website Protection Settings</a>
            <a href="#">Avoiding Data Breaches</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
    © 2026 Wix Help Center
</div>

</body>
</html>
